{"tid":1795491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[漢芯2.0] 強國兆芯公佈新型 CPU 規格　7nm 製程 + 支援 DDR5 + PCI-E 4.0","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:41:58.000Z","uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"da0a8dac18a2d47be37a743d99395895ee10d40c","tid":1795491,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"中國在近年一直希望在電子行業上減少對外國公司的依賴，自行研發出處理器以及系統，早前更正式開始試行 UOS 系統。近日，兆芯就被指目前正研發新款支援 x86 CPU 的晶片，並暫名為 KX-7000 系列，預計將支援 DDR5 記憶體以及 PCI-E 4.0，並有望會在 2021 年內發佈，與 Intel 和 AMD 兩大公司展開競爭。<br />\n<br />\n上海兆芯在今年 6 月的時候發佈了 KX-6000 系列的 x86 處理器，當中採用了 16nm 製程以及 SoC 設計，內部集成 CPU、GPU 內顯以及南橋晶片，主頻達到 3.0GHz ，並且支援雙通道 DDR4-3200 的記憶體。他們當時就公佈了最新的發展路線圖，預計明年將推出 KX-7000 系列，日前更透露了更多的消息。<br />\n<br />\n上海兆芯在日前宣佈新的 KX-7000 系列處理器將會以 7nm 製程生產，預計將支援 DDR5 記憶體以及 PCI-E 4.0，至於在 USB 規格他們就表示希望可以跟上目前主流的水準，而外媒就估計將會是USB 3.1 介面。官方亦未有詳細提及 KX-7000 的推出時間，但就指有望在 2021 年正式面世。<br />\n<br />\nsource:unwire<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/12/18/chinese-cpu/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F12%2F18%2Fchinese-cpu%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=c7c6c692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/12/18/chinese-cpu/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8c8f77ab244da865990a3973ec287db1f6200c","tid":1795491,"uid":284924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"究竟偷左幾多技術先做到出黎"},{"pid":"30fc4c70a573fad14b9309b8dd64c8b72db20c2e","tid":1795491,"uid":196751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"以前用半製成品砌埋叫自主研發<br />\n依加用元件砌埋叫自主研發<br />\n共產黨最叻自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2db1f28712fae71a624a1b9c6650cb4117412f","tid":1795491,"uid":230146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"有asml光刻機先再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea3e4a98afd692239e4d8346a2145cc02a3885e","tid":1795491,"uid":325884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:28:01.000Z","msg":"拆開個蓋原來係Intel Platinum 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單核單線程，待機50度，full load 95度，TDP 150watts<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0eae676ad0969f98491770fd45d668c9f19ca78","tid":1795491,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"今次唔知又磨走左邊粒CPU個LOGO喇"},{"pid":"b92a40c4e531d6c1a397a5cf7470e8a6bae78c3c","tid":1795491,"uid":43558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"兆芯 = VIA<br />\n7nm = 搵台仔或者韓仔造<br />\nDDR5 同 PCI-E 4 都係 license 返黎, 個 core 咪又係 VIA, 行得走得冇問題, IPC 打唔打得嬴 Atom 都成問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d75b10f701f0a5b7ab576c487a88ac38871ca7","tid":1795491,"uid":267494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"我行一轉黃金都可以自主研發一台商業用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0852c204ade0ede7d00639386a99be71e350b4a","tid":1795491,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d75b10f701f0a5b7ab576c487a88ac38871ca7","tid":1795491,"uid":267494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T0